description: Open October to March. Hosts competitions for local teams. Free entry, skate rental is 3chf for kids  and 5 for adults. Has a bistrot where you can get drinks and meals are served lunch time Wed - Sun and every evening until 11pm. Get down at the ice disco on Friday nights :)
